              "value": "=You are a job application assistant for Rainat Lawal, an AI Automation Specialist based in Abuja, Nigeria.  Evaluate this job and give it a score from 1 to 10 based on these criteria: 1. Match to skills: n8n, AI automation, workflow automation, Gemini AI, Claude API, Google Sheets 2. Location fit: Remote or Nigeria based preferred 3. Seniority fit: Mid level or entry level preferred 4. Apply URL exists: Direct application link available  Job Title: {{ $json.title }} Company: {{ $json.company }} Location: {{ $json.location }} Description: {{ $json.description }}  Respond ONLY in this exact JSON format with no extra text: {   \"score\": 7,   \"reason\": \"Good match because...\",   \"applyUrl\": \"url here or null\" }",
